<br>
Actually I remember going sword/shield and main tanking a lot up to level 20 (or whenever it was) when I got the njessie 2 hander and I stuck with 2 handers ever since and not had to be main tank so much since about then. However it does still happen, and can be okay if your not taking too many risks and you have a healer/shaman.<br>
<br>
Actually I mostly kill tasked up to level 20 rather then grouping (it was just when I did group I ended up main tank). Best way to get to 20 really when you have a skald as the speed lets you find your target in a short length of time. Heh, I've said it before and I'll say it again. Skalds - a group orientated class designed for soloing!<br>
<br>
Btw, expansion zones start areas are much much much much much much friendlier to totally new characters. You will get good drops even at low levels (level 1 mobs even drop non-magical unique armour, including studded), a hell of a lot more cash and the rags you pick up over there is pre-dyed so even total newbs can look good.<br>
<br>
Pop back at 5 and do the little cash tasks that were added in a while back (three dwarf helping tasks with good cash rewards in Mularn, Haggerfell and Auditen) and you should be pretty well set up.<br>
<br>
Sad thing is a lot of the earlier quests which were quite good still have the old, lame rewards (I always feel like that thrall keeper has spat in my hand, and that's nothing to the look I give that little Kobold in Vasudheim for making me swim all the way over to strider island and back (if I didn't know I'd get Riv off of the follow up quest I'd have killed him there and then). Also as you said the lowbie mobs in the main area don't drop as good loot as the ones in the expansion zone. Really it all needs to be brought in line (as I'm aware some people, possibly yourself, don't have the expansion). <p></p><i></i></td></tr></table><table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top"> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub36.ezboard.com/fteamskaldfrm7.showPrevMessage?topicID=27.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub36.ezboard.com/fteamskaldfrm7.showNextMessage?topicID=27.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br><a self href=http://pub36.ezboard.com/fteamskaldfrm7.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=27.topic&index=3><img src=http://www.stuckathome.com/skalded/images/addreply.gif border=0 alt="Add Reply"></a> </td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"> <a href=http://pub36.ezboard.com/fteamskaldfrm7.emailToFriend?topicID=27.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/image/email.gif border=0 alt="Email This To a Friend"> Email This To a Friend</a><br> <a href=http://pub36.ezboard.com/fteamskaldfrm7.threadControl?topicID=27.topic><img src=http://www.stuckathome.com/skalded/images/closethread.gif border=0 alt="Topic Control Image"> Topic Commands</a><br> <a href=http://pub36.ezboard.com/fteamskaldfrm7.subscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=27.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/ultimate/subscribe.gif width=20 height=20 border=0 alt="Click to receive email notification of replies"> Click to receive email notification of replies</a> <br>  <a href=http://pub36.ezboard.com/fteamskaldfrm7.